Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.97,0:02:06.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 和奏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.76,0:02:10.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.60,0:02:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.60,0:02:13.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難受嗎 痛不痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.39,0:02:15.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不然叫救護車吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.43,0:02:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 我估計是感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.42,0:02:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃藥了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.02,0:02:24.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用回來也沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.15,0:02:25.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了啦 躺一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.09,0:02:28.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去樓下鋪床
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.80,0:02:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.05,0:02:46.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.42,0:02:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是覺得痛或者難受
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.14,0:02:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼事都儘管說啊
