Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.17,0:03:07.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新學期開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.26,0:03:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,短暫的夏天雖然很快就過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.79,0:03:15.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你們的人生依然是春天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.82,0:03:18.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和奏沒來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.75,0:03:20.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師不是說她感冒了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.19,0:03:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是感冒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:26.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看她一直都沒什麼精神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.55,0:03:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擔心的話就發短信去問問呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.66,0:03:30.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是沒回應呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.84,0:03:32.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是因為來夏太煩...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.19,0:03:37.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...應該是想一個人靜靜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.59,0:03:50.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不睡著沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經沒事了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.85,0:03:52.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒在發燒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.48,0:03:55.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出了些汗 我去換身衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.75,0:03:56.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別勉強哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:03:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下周再去學校也沒事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.48,0:04:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.78,0:04:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的這樣就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.72,0:04:17.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 Step 01 (第一步）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.66,0:04:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是 好的發聲來自正確的姿勢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.62,0:04:23.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保持那個狀態 腰部用力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.55,0:04:25.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,緩慢向下...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 宮本呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.74,0:04:41.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果還是來了...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.22,0:04:43.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.67,0:04:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.36,0:05:16.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和奏？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:24.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和奏 不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.58,0:05:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和奏 不要啊！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:39.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來夏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.75,0:05:48.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感冒...沒事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.55,0:06:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點心意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.24,0:06:05.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紗羽出了一半的錢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.86,0:06:06.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.45,0:06:11.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,房間裡什麼都沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.17,0:06:13.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.09,0:06:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,榻榻米真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:22.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像在我爺爺家一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:24.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前說過麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.06,0:06:27.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爺爺超喜歡Conder Queens
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.38,0:06:29.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,經常一起唱歌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.82,0:06:33.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝了酒必定會提起過去演唱會的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.97,0:06:39.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後我就會雷打不動地大哭大鬧 「我也好想去」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:43.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每次他都會跟我約定下次一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.15,0:06:46.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最終還是沒能實現呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.77,0:06:50.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約定...不遵守不行呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.29,0:06:54.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也和媽媽約定過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.26,0:06:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽一直為了遵守約定而努力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.62,0:07:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而我因為毫不知情只顧著自己
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0,0,0,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.48,0:07:07.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼沒有把病情告訴我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.25,0:07:10.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是告訴我的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.71,0:07:18.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我現在覺得 幸好沒能實現約定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.91,0:07:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果實現了的話就結束了不是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.96,0:07:25.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因為還有約定才會經常想起爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.71,0:07:28.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「該死 沒有實現承諾」這樣想著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.23,0:07:31.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這也是重要的回憶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:40.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼歌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.96,0:07:42.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是媽媽的歌哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.51,0:07:43.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和奏的歌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.05,0:07:45.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有喲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.25,0:07:48.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己的歌必須自己來創作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.58,0:07:52.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是和奏不會創作歌曲呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.67,0:07:54.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼哪一天一起來創作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.59,0:07:58.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說好了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.03,0:07:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:04.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衣服洗乾淨了再還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.49,0:08:06.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼時候都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.84,0:08:09.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會不會暴露沒穿胸罩呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.27,0:08:11.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要再來玩喲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.59,0:08:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.35,0:08:17.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次請你吃白玉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.28,0:08:18.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 好期待呢
