Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.88,0:08:41.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次說的東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:48.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剪成企鵝的樣子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.82,0:08:50.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.92,0:08:53.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.49,0:08:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 路上小心喲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.99,0:08:58.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那心形呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.50,0:08:59.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說了不行了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:03.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:05.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和奏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.37,0:09:07.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.62,0:09:09.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給 照片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.59,0:09:12.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.73,0:09:14.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有這個
