Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.50,0:09:17.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,錄音帶？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.15,0:09:20.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合唱大賽之前大家錄的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:23.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以聽到媽媽的聲音呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.73,0:09:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽也曾經可愛過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.30,0:09:31.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惜 現在已經是不同的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.50,0:09:32.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.25,0:09:38.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 和奏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.54,0:09:39.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來有空嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.61,0:09:43.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿著韁繩把手放到馬鞍上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.11,0:09:45.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腳放在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.75,0:09:46.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是這隻腳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.55,0:09:47.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然就面朝後了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:48.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.62,0:09:50.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一二
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.71,0:09:55.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好高
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.38,0:09:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,景色看起來完全不一樣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.93,0:09:59.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.06,0:10:00.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那開始走了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.21,0:10:03.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢點兒...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:07.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雙腿用夾著薩布萊背部的感覺來取得平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.33,0:10:08.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.13,0:10:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薩布萊是紗羽的馬嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.22,0:10:13.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 先是爸爸的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.02,0:10:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年呢 我要騎著薩布萊參賽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.20,0:10:21.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爸爸是剛才開助動車的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.04,0:10:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.90,0:10:25.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸反對我成為騎手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.23,0:10:28.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至還說不繼承寺院的話就去當公務員好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.38,0:10:29.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不跟他說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.02,0:10:35.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是要是從此不能見面的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.18,0:10:38.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就永遠停留在吵架狀態了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.66,0:10:42.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要稍微跑跑看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.37,0:10:44.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.44,0:10:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把背部挺直
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.21,0:10:49.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保持好的節奏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.58,0:10:50.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要拉韁繩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.45,0:10:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放鬆點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.68,0:10:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:10:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太快了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.13,0:11:01.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是滿費力氣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.08,0:11:05.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薩布萊很中意和奏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.38,0:11:06.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.63,0:11:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再來騎喲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.43,0:11:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.48,0:11:19.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.81,0:11:25.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銅鑼 和奏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:31.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有要緊事所以先出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.24,0:11:33.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早飯在微波爐裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.94,0:11:34.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出發了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0,0,0,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:08.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.90,0:12:19.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用秘密晨練讓來夏她們大吃一驚大作戰失敗了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.32,0:12:22.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是驚到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.77,0:12:24.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想幫到大家的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.42,0:12:26.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以希望能唱得好一點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.78,0:12:27.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和奏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:30.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你認為我們首先需要的是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.59,0:12:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,常識？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.38,0:12:34.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說了就只有我們是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.56,0:12:48.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在生氣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.85,0:12:49.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.80,0:12:52.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露出那麼可怕的表情 唱著啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.71,0:12:56.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是 那是為了唱準音程
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.86,0:12:59.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發聲練習也要當做唱歌來進行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.19,0:13:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肩膀放鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.47,0:13:06.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 和奏最喜歡的人在遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.18,0:13:12.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懷著把「我很好」的心情傳達出去的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.12,0:13:22.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 心情是很重要的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:25.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然只靠書是不會明白的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.03,0:13:31.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.81,0:13:35.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 高橋老師的孩子出生了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.43,0:13:36.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.30,0:13:38.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是個女孩喲
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0,0,0,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:39.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.65,0:13:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,田中君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.80,0:13:43.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前的羽毛球賽沒去給你加油對不起了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.63,0:13:44.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.89,0:13:45.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.41,0:13:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,輪不到你說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.11,0:13:50.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來 她是來做什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.71,0:13:51.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0,0,0,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
